# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-06-02 11:43

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:17
translate portuguese adrian3b_bdd6187c:

    # "I sit down at the computer and install the game that Adrian had bought for me."
    "Sento-me ao computador e instalo o jogo que a Adrian comprou para mim."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:18
translate portuguese adrian3b_3e2f7daf:

    # "It doesn't take too long, then it is on my desktop."
    "Não demora muito tempo e já está no meu ambiente de trabalho."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:19
translate portuguese adrian3b_e481cbc4:

    # "I guess I'll give it a try."
    "Acho que vou experimentar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:21
translate portuguese adrian3b_8131ccda:

    # "I start up the game and choose the server that Adrian had written down for me so that we could play together."
    "Inicio o jogo e escolho o servidor que a Adrian me tinha anotado para que pudéssemos jogar juntos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:22
translate portuguese adrian3b_62dfcc6e:

    # "First thing I have to do is create a character."
    "A primeira coisa que tenho de fazer é criar uma personagem."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:24
translate portuguese adrian3b_59517f82:

    # "I spend probably too much time going through all the different options, before deciding on the character I want to play."
    "Provavelmente demoro demasiado tempo a analisar todas as opções diferentes, antes de decidir qual a personagem que quero jogar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:25
translate portuguese adrian3b_827389d1:

    # "I know that Adrian is playing a magic-user, so I want to go with something more physical and melee-focused."
    "Sei que a Adrian está a jogar com uma feiticeira, por isso quero optar por algo mais físico e focado no combate corpo a corpo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:27
translate portuguese adrian3b_c19763c8:

    # "I end up going with a half-orc warrior. I like the idea of fighting all these enemies up close and personal."
    "Acabo por escolher um guerreiro meio-orco. Gosto da ideia de lutar contra todos estes inimigos de perto e pessoalmente."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:28
translate portuguese adrian3b_112c09f7:

    # "He is also the biggest, most badass character that I could make."
    "Ele é também a personagem mais grande e mais durona que eu poderia criar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:30
translate portuguese adrian3b_8f0fae1d:

    # "I turn up the volume and start the game."
    "Aumento o volume e inicio o jogo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:31
translate portuguese adrian3b_4d69dd27:

    # "After a little intro movie, it drops me into the world."
    "Após um pequeno vídeo de introdução, sou lançado para o mundo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:32
translate portuguese adrian3b_62775756:

    # "I wonder if Adrian is online right now? She said she would be. I type her username into the search window and find her."
    "Será que a Adrian está online neste momento? Ela disse que estaria. Digito o nome de utilizador dela na janela de pesquisa e encontro-a."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:33
translate portuguese adrian3b_03467b31:

    # "So I send her a voicechat request, which she answers almost immediately."
    "Então, envio-lhe um pedido de chat de voz, ao qual ela responde quase imediatamente."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:35
translate portuguese adrian3b_a3f59b75:

    # gg "[pcname]! You're here!"
    gg "[pcname]! Estás aqui!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:36
translate portuguese adrian3b_589ce956:

    # pc "I'm here. Hey, Adrian."
    pc "Estou aqui. Olá, Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:37
translate portuguese adrian3b_0ec64e72:

    # gg "Where are you right now?"
    gg "Onde estás neste momento?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:38
translate portuguese adrian3b_2730945b:

    # pc "I'm not sure. Wherever you start as with a half-orc."
    pc "Não tenho a certeza. Onde quer que se comece com um meio-orco."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:39
translate portuguese adrian3b_3292efd3:

    # gg "Oh, you're in Arigamir. Okay, I'll teleport there in just a minute."
    gg "Ah, estás em Arigamir. Ok, vou teletransportar-me para lá num minuto."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:40
translate portuguese adrian3b_b9029897:

    # pc "Okay. I'm just doing some of this tutorial stuff."
    pc "Ok. Estou só a fazer algumas coisas do tutorial."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:43
translate portuguese adrian3b_0520cb55:

    # "After a minute or so, Adrian's character \"Trenoxa\", who I recognize from playing before walks up to me."
    "Passado um minuto ou assim, a personagem da Adrian, «Trenoxa», que reconheço de ter jogado antes, aproxima-se de mim."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:44
translate portuguese adrian3b_2116c262:

    # gg "Wow, you're a big guy, huh?"
    gg "Uau, és um tipo grande, não és?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:45
translate portuguese adrian3b_55e9779d:

    # pc "Yeah, I wanted to play a big melee character."
    pc "Sim, queria jogar com uma personagem grande de combate corpo a corpo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:46
translate portuguese adrian3b_fd3dc2df:

    # gg "Well I'm not complaining."
    gg "Bem, não me estou a queixar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:47
translate portuguese adrian3b_33a9a8b1:

    # gg "Want to go kill some stuff?"
    gg "Queres ir matar algumas coisas?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:48
translate portuguese adrian3b_39757b54:

    # pc "Yeah, let's do it."
    pc "Sim, vamos a isso."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:51
translate portuguese adrian3b_c06aa83e:

    # "We spend the next hour or so doing various quests, killing monsters, and leveling up."
    "Passamos a hora seguinte a fazer várias missões, a matar monstros e a subir de nível."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:52
translate portuguese adrian3b_44e05c13:

    # "She shows me the world a bit, shows me how to advance my character, and gives me a bunch of equipment to start with."
    "Ela mostra-me um pouco do mundo, ensina-me como fazer a minha personagem avançar e dá-me um monte de equipamento para começar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:53
translate portuguese adrian3b_606b69f6:

    # "Who needs a tutorial when I have her?"
    "Quem precisa de um tutorial quando a tenho a ela?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:56
translate portuguese adrian3b_40c77f2c:

    # "Then we head back to the Inn, a place called \"The Feedmill\", and sit down for a drink together."
    "Depois voltamos para a pousada, um lugar chamado «The Feedmill», e sentamo-nos para tomar uma bebida juntos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:57
translate portuguese adrian3b_4a42f78f:

    # pc "That was really fun."
    pc "Foi muito divertido."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:58
translate portuguese adrian3b_e7c80669:

    # gg "I'm glad you enjoyed it. I had a blast."
    gg "Ainda bem que gostaste. Eu diverti-me imenso."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:59
translate portuguese adrian3b_31f7576c:

    # pc "Me too. I should be careful though. I could see myself really getting addicted to this game."
    pc "Eu também. Mas tenho de ter cuidado. Consigo ver-me a ficar mesmo viciado neste jogo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:60
translate portuguese adrian3b_0233efaf:

    # gg "You don't have to tell me about that. I play way too much."
    gg "Não precisas de me dizer isso. Eu jogo demais."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:61
translate portuguese adrian3b_2d5d032d:

    # gg "It's good to play in short bursts though. Don't spend all day on here, you know?"
    gg "Mas é bom jogar em sessões curtas. Não passes o dia todo aqui, percebes?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:62
translate portuguese adrian3b_7acad64a:

    # pc "Right."
    pc "Certo."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:63
translate portuguese adrian3b_79845768:

    # gg "Well, we should probably get off for today then, but I hope you'll come on here and play again with me soon."
    gg "Bem, acho que devemos sair por hoje, mas espero que voltes aqui para jogares comigo em breve."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:64
translate portuguese adrian3b_95e44169:

    # pc "I will. Thanks for showing me the ropes."
    pc "Vou voltar. Obrigado por me mostrares como funciona."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:65
translate portuguese adrian3b_b6875399:

    # gg "No problem. Keep fighting like that and you'll be max level in no time."
    gg "De nada. Continua a lutar assim e vais atingir o nível máximo num instante."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:66
translate portuguese adrian3b_d91c0c89:

    # gg "I'll see you later, [pcname]."
    gg "Até logo, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:69
translate portuguese adrian3b_f4460497:

    # "With that, we log off together."
    "Com isso, saímos juntos."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:2
    old "After Adrian gives you a copy of Souls of War to play with her,"
    new "Depois de a Adrian te dar uma cópia do Souls of War para jogares com ela,"

    # game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian3b.rpy:3
    old "install it on the computer in your bedroom and play with her at night."
    new "instala-o no computador do teu quarto e joga com ela à noite."

